Description:
**This game will NOT run well on low end devices!**

Twisted is a storm chasing game by Willzuh and Siryzm.

Throughout the rolling hills and prairies of the fictional state of Keysota, scientists and thrill seekers alike set out on the roads in chase of severe weather. Some will observe from a safe distance, while others will risk it all to get the perfect shot of a violent tornado from close range. Whether you're out there deploying data-collecting probes, intercepting in an armored vehicle, or just taking pictures, you're bound to have a run in with mother nature like no other. Just watch yourself, sometimes the hunters become the hunted. 

Connect with us through our social links (below this), where you can talk to others about the game, view change logs, announcements, and make suggestions.

Name: Sinking Ship BUT WITH REALISTIC WATER PHYSICS!
Description:
The first ever sinking ship game on Roblox to have "interactive interior water physics" for all of the rooms on the ship! Experience and survive a sinking ship in a way you've never experienced before!

Just to be clear, the "realistic" part refers to the fact that rooms can flood separately.

cool features:
-Air pockets!
-Opening doors will cause the room to flood if there is water outside the room!
-Glass and Doors can sometimes break under water pressure, causing an unstoppable rush of water so beware!
-You can toggle the walls and underwater fog in the settings to see the water level physics clearly in action!
-The ship may sink a little faster the more rooms that are flooded!

Technical:
Having realistic terrain water is not possible because terrain water is "voxel-based" and plus will just cause more lag. Blocky water is all we can get for now but other than that, enjoy those glorious physics and air pockets!

When you finally get there, everything around you bursts into bright, happy colors, just like a real rainbow, making you feel like you‚Äôre in a fairy tale. The hidden path leads to a place full of amazing beauty and fun. Doing a hard obstacle course, or obby, can be really challenging but also super fun! You have to climb, jump, and balance on all sorts of tricky parts. Sometimes you might fall, but you get back up and try again. Each time you get a little better and move a little farther. Name: Anarchy Chess
Description:
Chess but multiplayer and chaotic It starts off pretty mild *usually*, till people are checking the king through two sets of portals onto a nuke that would explode half of white's position while the void is eating your queen and the other half of your pieces are on fire. Also if the server is full, you'll see pawns begging for mercy, people calling each other stupid and then being sacked by the voting hivemind and some poor rook in the corner that will end up losing before they can move and some people voting to sacrifice the king, so, pretty fun, bring some popcorn.

Updates:

* Made all servers 200 players big cause why not

* Duels exist (1v1 on this chess board against a another player), if you are into that kinda thing

* Fixed that random chat bug where the bubble chats would be strange
* Buffed freezer

* New mid round events: "Add sniper" and "Add building supplies" which allow your team to choose which player to shot and where to place walls if you land on it.
